## Commands (:)
Close current view|:q / :quit
Force close, ignore unsaved changes|:q! / :quit!
Open a file from disk|:o / :open <file>
Close current buffer|:bc / :buffer-close
Write changes to disk|:w / :write
Force write, create subdirectories|:w!
Write all buffers to disk|:wa / :write-all
Write and quit|:wq
Write all and quit all views|:wqa / :write-quit-all
Quit all views|:qa / :quit-all
Force quit all views|:qa!
Create new scratch buffer|:new
Format file using LSP formatter|:fmt / :format
Set indentation style|:set-indent <t or 1-8>
Set line ending (crlf or lf)|:set-line-ending <mode>
Jump back in edit history|:earlier <steps or time>
Jump forward in edit history|:later <steps or time>
Change current working directory|:cd <path>
Show current working directory|:pwd
Reload from source file|:reload
Reload all documents|:reload-all
Change theme|:theme <name>
Set language of current buffer|:lang <name>
Set config option at runtime|:set <option> <value>
Toggle boolean config option|:toggle <option>
Get current value of config option|:get <option>
Sort ranges in selection|:sort
Sort ranges in selection (reverse)|:rsort
Goto line number|:goto <n>
Restart language server|:lsp-restart
Stop language server|:lsp-stop
Open user config.toml|:config-open
Open workspace config.toml|:config-open-workspace
Refresh user config|:config-reload
Open helix log file|:log-open
Hard-wrap current selection to width|:reflow [width]
Clear register (or all if no arg)|:reg-clear [reg]
Run shell command|:sh <cmd>
